WEBVTT

00:00.141 --> 00:01.679
You need to watch out
for yourselves out here.

00:01.690 --> 00:02.924
Father?

00:03.851 --> 00:06.270
If I thought you were
exploiting my grief

00:06.282 --> 00:09.593
just to gain license
to practice your sorcery...

00:09.604 --> 00:11.952
Young man, you have
no idea what you have done!

00:16.488 --> 00:18.366
You will leave the palace tonight.

00:18.390 --> 00:20.861
If you ever return
your life is forfeit.

00:22.112 --> 00:24.296
I'm sorry.

00:26.000 --> 00:32.073
